            <div type="transcript" id="F532A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Winters are so short -</l>
                    <l>I'm hardly justified </l>
                    <l>In sending all the Birds away - </l>
                    <l>And moving into Pod - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Myself - for scarcely settled -</l>
                    <l>The Phebes have begun - </l>
                    <l>And then - it's time to strike<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 my Tent - </l>
                    <l>And open House - again - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It's mostly, interruptions - </l>
                    <l>My Summer - is despoiled -</l>
                    <l>Because there was a Winter -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 once - </l>
                    <l>And all the Cattle - starved -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And so there was a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Deluge - </l>
                    <l>And swept the World<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 away - </l>
                    <l>But Ararat's a Legend - now -</l>
                    <l>And no one credits Noah - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
